@Cherry 

GESTE is one you need to remember.  It has appeared 130 times, including 25 times when the clue was "Beau ____", and many others, like today's, when the clue was that plus added information.  It has rarely been clued any other way.  BEAU, of course, has rarely been clued to the novel, since there are other ways to clue it.

The combination of common letters makes GESTE a handy word for constructors.  Put it in your back pocket!

